    "In this study, the LLMs were asked about pairing or interaction between drugs, and their responses are evaluated in terms of correctness and conclusiveness.",
    "Among the 40 pairs of Drug-Drug-Interactions, 39 responses are correct for the first question, and among these 39 correct answers, 19 are conclusive while 20 are inconclusive.",
